    <body>
        <p>Specifies the severity level of unexpected content in the drift report. Valid values are <code>INFO</code> (<code>0</code>), <code>MINOR</code> (<code>1</code>), <code>MAJOR</code> (<code>2</code>), <code>CRITICAL</code> (<code>3</code>), and <code>BLOCKER</code> (<code>4</code>), from least severe to most severe. Overrides the value of <code>--drift-severity</code> for unexpected content only. <b>Default: <code>INFO</code></b>.</p>
    </body>
</html>